commit.message: Update files for 2.3.0 release.
Change wording of "signature database is not enabled" error message.
Fix order of cache operations to match description in man page.
Add --cached option to speed up matching against files previously scanned.
Use proper punctuation for command-line argument definitions in manpage.
Fix typo in manpage.
Employ nanosecond precision for stat(), if supported.
Clarify error message for improper usage 'fdupes [directory] --recurse:'.
Add copyright notice to removeifnotchanged .c and .h files.

Set _XOPEN_SOURCE to 700 to get strcasecmp on OpenBSD.

(via omar-polo, pull request #170)

Fix the return type of cmd_prune.

(via omar-polo, pull request #170)

Include wctype.h for isw* functions.

(via omar-polo, pull request #170)
Update version number to 2.2.1 and indicate changes.
Bugfix: don't compare files against logfile_status when log file not open.
